  "ext_description": {
    "message": "Brings every OmniRoute provider (:20128) into one window: web-session capture (incl. HttpOnly cookies), API-key entry (170+), all OAuth flows (device code / browser login / token paste). An honest live check of every connection plus background health monitoring. The catalog is generated from OmniRoute's own source."
  },
